Ranger Help for: use herbs
===========================

SYNTAX:      apply <herb> [to <target>]
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  healing

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to apply gathered herbs to heal wounds or
cure ailments. Different herbs have different effects, and a skilled
Ranger learns to identify and use them effectively. The Ranger can
apply herbs to themselves or to another player. The effectiveness of
the treatment depends on the Ranger's wisdom, skill level, and the
quality of the herbs used. Herbs can be found through foraging.
